  "summary": "specify size of the text in points. <normalsize> applies to point label, <smallsize> applies to remark and all other point labels. Each of them may apply to line label according to its -scale option. The defaults are 8 10 12 16 24 for scales upto 1:100; 7 8 10 14 20 for scales upto 1:200; 6 7 8 10 14 for scales upto 1:500 and 5 6 7 8 10 for scales smaller than 1:500.",
